content: I'm being bullied by the app to write more often, AND I LOVE IT! I love the notifs that remind me to write and the app is easy to use and full of great ideas!

content: Writing against time, just the app I wanted! Whoop whoop üéâ üéä ‚ú®

This is a cool concept, but the prompts aren't really all that great. They're generally vague and not worth spending a dollar on. There are websites you can use where you set an amount of time you wanna have to write and go from there, and those are free - I'd recommend checking a few of them out before you spend money on a mediocre app like this.
replyContent: Hey, Elliot! Thank you for your review. Websites which have free prompts do exist. But in this app you can save prompts & write in the app itself, so you don't need even need internet to see prompts & write, unlike websites. If you have suggestions to improve the app, please write to us at : writingpromptsapp@gmail.com. We would love to hear! :)
